reviewText:
THIS BOOK IS ABOUT ENGLISH STEAM TRACTION ENGINES, THOUGH THERE ARE PRETTY WOMEN, ONE
OF WHO ACTUALLY DRIVES ONE OF THESE HUGE TRACTORS! FOR STEAM ENTHUSIASTS, THIS IS A
CUTE/CLEVER COMEDY BUILT AROUND A TRACTION ENGINE MEET IN ENGLAND, SHOWING A NUMBER
OF DIFFERENT_RESTORED STEAM POWERED TRACTORS!
I saw this movie on the big screen and it i just as good now as it was then. There is nothing like British comedy.
